---
title: "Sidan hittades inte"
description: "404-sida för Stödlinjer Sverige"
permalink: "/404.html"
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
pageClass: "solid-bg-shell"
header:
  icon: "compass"
  label: "Hitta rätt"
  title: "404 – sidan finns inte"
  subtitle: "Länken du följde verkar inte fungera. Vi guidar dig tillbaka till rätt stöd."
  links:
    - url: "/"
      icon: "home"
      text: "Startsida"
      aria: "Till startsidan"
    - url: "/artiklar/"
      icon: "newsletter"
      text: "Artiklar"
      aria: "Till artiklar och guider"
    - url: "/kontakt/"
      icon: "envelope-letter"
      text: "Kontakt"
      aria: "Kontakta oss"
---

{% extends "layouts/base.njk" %}
{% from "partials/icon.njk" import icon %}

{% block header %}
  {% include "partials/header.njk" %}
{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-10 sm:py-14">
    <div class="surface-card strong-card overflow-hidden">
      <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-[1.2fr_1fr]">
        <div class="p-7 sm:p-9">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-5">
            <span class="pill">{{ icon('compass') }} Felsteg</span>
            <span class="stat-chip">{{ icon('warning-circle') }} 404</span>
          </div>

          <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">
            Hoppsan, vi hittar inte sidan
          </h1>
          <p class="text-lg muted mb-6">
            Länken kan vara gammal eller felstavad. Använd genvägarna nedan för att snabbt hitta rätt stödlinje.
          </p>

          <div class="grid gap-3 sm:gap-4">
            <a
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-between gap-3 px-4 py-3 rounded-lg bg-[var(--accent)] text-white font-semibold shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition"
              href="{{ baseUrl }}/"
            >
              <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2">{{ icon('arrow-left') }} Till startsidan</span>
              {{ icon('compass') }}
            </a>
            <a
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-between gap-3 px-4 py-3 rounded-lg bg-[var(--card)] text-[var(--text)] font-semibold border border-[var(--border)] hover:border-[var(--accent)] transition"
              href="{{ baseUrl }}/artiklar/"
            >
              <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2">{{ icon('newsletter') }} Utforska guider och artiklar</span>
              {{ icon('book-open') }}
            </a>
            <a
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-between gap-3 px-4 py-3 rounded-lg bg-[var(--card)] text-[var(--text)] font-semibold border border-[var(--border)] hover:border-[var(--accent)] transition"
              href="{{ baseUrl }}/kontakt/"
            >
              <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2">{{ icon('envelope-letter') }} Kontakta oss</span>
              {{ icon('chat-bubble-dots') }}
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-b from-[var(--accent-soft)] to-[var(--card)] p-7 sm:p-9 flex flex-col gap-5 border-t md:border-t-0 md:border-l border-[var(--border)]">
          <div class="pill w-fit">{{ icon('life-ring') }} Snabbhjälp</div>
          <p class="text-base muted">
            Spara de viktigaste numren eller dela dem med någon som behöver stöd direkt.
          </p>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-3">
            <a
              href="tel:90101"
              class="surface-card p-4 rounded-lg flex justify-between items-center hover:shadow-glow transition"
              aria-label="Ring Självmordslinjen 90101"
            >
              <div>
                <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--accent)] flex items-center gap-2">
                  {{ icon('headset-1') }} Självmordslinjen
                </p>
                <p class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 dark:text-white phone-number">90101</p>
              </div>
              <span class="badge-urgent">Öppet dygnet runt</span>
            </a>

            <a
              href="tel:112"
              class="surface-card p-4 rounded-lg flex justify-between items-center hover:shadow-glow transition"
              aria-label="Ring SOS Alarm 112"
            >
              <div>
                <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--accent)] flex items-center gap-2">
                  {{ icon('sos') }} SOS Alarm
                </p>
                <p class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 dark:text-white phone-number">112</p>
              </div>
              <span class="badge-urgent">Vid akut fara</span>
            </a>

            <a
              href="tel:020505050"
              class="surface-card p-4 rounded-lg flex justify-between items-center hover:shadow-glow transition"
              aria-label="Ring Kvinnofridslinjen 020-505050"
            >
              <div>
                <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--accent)] flex items-center gap-2">
                  {{ icon('cross-shield-2') }} Kvinnofridslinjen
                </p>
                <p class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 dark:text-white phone-number">020-505050</p>
              </div>
              <span class="tag">Våld &amp; hot</span>
            </a>
          </div>

          <p class="text-sm muted mb-0">
            Behöver du hjälp att hitta rätt stödlinje?
            <a class="inline-link font-semibold" href="{{ baseUrl }}/">Börja på startsidan</a>
            eller
            <a class="inline-link font-semibold" href="{{ baseUrl }}/kontakt/">hör av dig</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
{% endblock %}
